  "authors": [],
  "body": {
    "comment": "EMURGO as a DRep votes ABSTAIN on Reforming Treasury Governance, with rationale outlined below.\n\nThis proposal touches on foundational governance architecture that warrants careful deliberation. The scope of the proposed changes is broad, and EMURGO believes that decisions of this nature benefit from wider community input and a more structured review process before DReps commit to a position. EMURGO abstains at this stage and will engage further as the discussion matures."
  },
  "hashAlgorithm": "blake2b-256"
}